Reproducing Paper Results
Run the following commands to reproduce key results:
Result	Command
Main results (Table 2)	python evaluate.py --config configs/bmtdl.yaml --table main
Ablation studies (Table 4)	python evaluate.py --config configs/ablation.yaml --table ablation
Uncertainty analysis (Figure 2)	python visualize.py --analysis uncertainty
Causal graphs (Figure 4)	python visualize.py --analysis causal --patient_id 123
